snippet.title: Teaser After Fright Fangame_Horizons Event
snippet.description:
We are happy to announce that we will be at the Fangame_Horizons event prepared with a reveal trailer for the game. 

Game: https://gamejolt.com/games/after-fright/718069

We also announced that we have voice for Chica, Mangle and Springtrap. Things are coming. 

See you there 😎
